on\">ORCL</a></span>) </strong>recently announced fiscal <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4379898-oracle-non-gaap-eps-of-1_47-misses-0_01-revenue-of-14_1b-misses-20m\">Q2 results</a>, which did not satisfy the investors, as the shares slumped over 8% on the market open. The demand for its cloud infrastructure and services is robust, and the pipeline is healthy. However, it</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1867844462/image_1867844462.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743331-oracle-q2-great-cloud-performance-valuation-stretched", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 19:30:25"}, {"id": "4743321", "title": "CVS Health: When The Industry Is In Crisis, Don't Pick The Weaker Players", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"People shopping at CVS / pharmacy\" data-id=\"1166290360\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166290360/image_1166290360.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" 